{"tid":1979106,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"吉野家突棄租油麻地店 業主轟欠租逾四個月","createTime":"2020-04-19T07:47:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T04:40:21.000Z","uid":4007,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0c82acf1686126ec519d5869cee1c10e09cddd11","tid":1979106,"uid":4007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T07:47:53.000Z","msg":"連鎖快餐店吉野家位於油麻地彌敦道524號僑江大廈的分店日前結業，據門外業主貼出告示，指吉野家自去年12月起欠租，4月8日向業主發信將歸還店舖，並於9日將分店鎖匙送到業主辦公室。本報就事件向香港吉野家查詢，暫未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n根據資料，該店業主私人公司 Master Cosmos International Limited，由本地著名物業投資者冠華鏡廠家族持有。業主在告示中指出，行動未經其同意，吉野家的行為將會視為提早終止租約，業主將會執行權利，重新進入及取得該店舖的所有權，業主將所有的貨物、裝備等，相關費用將由吉野家承擔。<br />\n<br />\n日前有本地傳媒報道，該分店建築面積約2922方呎，月租26.8萬元，租約尚餘一年半，現以每月24.8萬元放租，較吉野家的月租低逾7%。吉野家早於2009年已租用上址作為分店，最初月租11.5萬元，多年來已累積加租1.3倍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1587282151800&amp;issue=20200419\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1587282151800%26issue%3D20200419&d=BjPUJoueJJBj8huYKMWPWlJiVKGJ8LWvq%2BeQg4NrPGo%3D&h=853b14e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1587282151800&amp;issue=20200419</a>"},{"pid":"b7fc45f782ea52e805419ce5f323db0abce3f5ff","tid":1979106,"uid":6435,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T07:53:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />WIN"},{"pid":"88e853d89272f52e01944c75cf0fdb9562222771","tid":1979106,"uid":62749,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T07:55:59.000Z","msg":"唔怪得仲未執，靠唔找數頂住?<br />\n會唔會差落成街街數，間間鋪都欠租"},{"pid":"3bb97505c7dc34c1161f45d2a9f2b55fb831f7cb","tid":1979106,"uid":259010,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"ci